title: Hands On: Tumi Chambers Slim Card Case - 12659
description:
Tumi Chambers Atlantic Slim Card Case - 12659 - Atlantic 
http://www.abt.com/product/102220/Tumi-Chambers-Slim-Card-Case-12659HUNTER.html?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=video&utm_campaign=12659HUNTER_20160708

Taking you from work to weekend the Chambers collection of wallets and accessories is handcrafted from supple and smooth goatskin. The interior of each piece is distinguished by a subtle contrast edging detail. Features include Tumi ID Lock™ a proprietary technology designed to protect personal data encoded on most IDs credit cards and passports. This card case features card slots on the front and back and a hidden interior compartment. Comes in an elegant gift box.
